&reftitle.resources;
This extension defines the following resource types:
List of resource types in GD
Name Description Notes
gd Image resource, used by functions like imagecreatefrompng Prior to PHP 8.0.0
gd font Font resource internally created by imageloadfont Prior to PHP 8.1.0
